One for All — with the @Anycubic Official Wash&Cure Max, you can wash and cure your models with just one click.

If you’ve ever visited Gulliver’s Gate in New York or other similar museum of miniatures in other countries, and wondered how it all is created, then in this 18-minute video we will show you a very small part of the entire process:

When we started working on the first three miniatures of the series last year, we decided to record the process of working on one of them. Filming and editing took us 5 months in total. The work is truly enormous, level of details amazes everyone who sees miniature in real. Proud of our Minibricks team!
